snippet.title: IKARO Will Not Die | Announce Teaser
snippet.description:
From Futurlab, the award-winning creators of Powerwash Simulator and Velocity, in partnership with Thunderful, comes IKARO, a momentum-based, fast-flowing action rogue-lite.
